metadata.name: APOPHIS
metadata.description:
"He, the great Ra,
Kills the evil serpent
Breaks his spine
And the fire devours him."
Book of the Dead

Asteroid "APOPHIS" ​​- named after the mythical serpent Apophis - the destroyer of worlds, with whom the god Ra fights. Asteroid is one of the most dangerous for our planet. 

2004 MN₄ (99942)
